text: Services & Solutions: At Nexora Technologies, we offer a wide range of technical services designed to meet the ever-evolving needs of modern businesses. Our services are built around innovation, agility, and scalability — ensuring that every solution delivers measurable value and long-term impact. 1. Custom Software Development We build web and mobile applications from the ground up, tailored to specific business workflows and customer expectations. Our developers specialize in scalable, API-driven architectures using modern frameworks such as React, Angular, Flutter, Node.js, Django, and Laravel. 2. AI & Machine Learning Our data scientists help companies unlock the power of artificial intelligence. From recommendation engines and fraud detection to sentiment analysis and predictive modeling, we build AI systems that learn and adapt to business behavior. 3. Cloud & DevOps Whether you're just beginning your cloud journey or looking to scale an existing infrastructure, Nexora provides cloud architecture, migration, and optimization services. We’re proficient in AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud. Our DevOps team builds CI/CD pipelines, sets up infrastructure-as-code (IaC), and ensures smooth container orchestration using Docker and Kubernetes. 4. Data Engineering & Business Intelligence Data is only valuable when it’s accessible and actionable. We design and implement ETL pipelines, data lakes, and

analytical dashboards that empower clients to make informed decisions. Tools we use include Apache Airflow, Snowflake, Power BI, and Looker. 5. API Integration & Microservices We enable seamless communication between services by building secure APIs and microservice architectures. This ensures modularity, easy scaling, and better system performance. 6. Technical Consulting & Support Beyond development, we guide our clients on product roadmaps, architecture decisions, compliance, and security best practices. We provide ongoing support, upgrades, and SLA-based maintenance for long-term success. Our service model is highly collaborative — we work closely with stakeholders through agile sprints and frequent demos. This transparency and flexibility ensure we deliver what the client actually needs, not just what was initially scoped.
